GraphData.Name: 4 SC20 Move Z Collimator
GraphData.Kommentar: Use the IDM measurement to send the Z-collimator result. The defocus parameter simply gets added to the Z-collimator result. That means, if a positive value is specified, the focus will move away from the part, towards the welding head. If a negative value is being used, the focus will shift into the part
